title: 300 Rise Of An Empire 720p (greek subs) by kozanitis
description:
Eida tin tainia auti kai mou fanike kalyteri apo tin proti. Epomenos an sas arese i proti tainia ki auti tha sas aresei oposdipote.

I eikona einai poly kali kai o ixos episis. Gi auto sas tin prosfero me ellinikouw ypotitlous se analysi 720p: 1280x636 gia na tin apolausete stin tileorasi saa.

Mono elattoma oi kinezikoi ypotitloi, pou omos den enoxloun stin anagnosi ton ellinikon.

Kali diaskedasi.
